.DT 
query_skill 
Discworld living help 
query_skill 

Name
.SI 5
query_skill - Returns the level of the skill.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
int query_skill(string skill);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
What level is the player in the skill bing?  This is the function that
will tell you this devastingly useful information.  It is a straight level,
this is not modified by race or any other strange thingys.  This should
not be used as a skill success checking function.  Use the 
query_skill_bonus for that.  This function makes use of the level
cache.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_skill_bonus, query_skills, query_level_cache
.EP
